+ (( i++ ))
+ (( i < n_routers ))
+ router_i=(${routers[$i]})
+ rname=MUNI

+ property2=host:miniinterneteth/d_host
++ echo host:miniinterneteth/d_host
++ cut -d : -f 1
+ htype=host
++ echo host:miniinterneteth/d_host
++ cut -d : -f 2
+ dname=miniinterneteth/d_host
+ [[ ! -z miniinterneteth/d_host ]]
+ [[ host == *\r\o\u\t\i\n\a\t\o\r* ]]
+ [[ host == *\k\r\i\l\l* ]]
+ (( i++ ))
+ (( i < n_routers ))
+ router_i=(${routers[$i]})
+ rname=LYON
+ property1=MATRIX
+ property2=host:miniinterneteth/d_host

+ htype=host

+ dname=miniinterneteth/d_host
